Bu papka Alembic migratsiyalari uchun.

Yangi migratsiya yaratish (modellar o'zgargach):
    docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.bot.yml run --rm bot \
        alembic revision --autogenerate -m "ozgarish tavsifi"

Migratsiyalarni qo'llash:
    docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.bot.yml run --rm bot \
        alembic upgrade head

Bir qadam orqaga qaytarish:
    ... alembic downgrade -1

Eslatma: bot konteyneri ishga tushganda entrypoint.sh avtomatik
`alembic upgrade head` ni bajaradi.
